Henry Juszkiewicz, chief executive 
officer of Gibson Guitar Corp., says the company's business and 
its market share are growing. Juszkiewicz talks with Bloomberg's
 Tom Keene , Scarlet Fu and Sara Eisen on Bloomberg Radio's 
"Bloomberg Surveillance."     (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 04:56
 